WEBVTT

00:00.584 --> 00:02.794
- Who are you talking about?
- He's in a coma, David!

00:03.170 --> 00:05.589
- Who?
- Justin, Ricci.

00:07.090 --> 00:09.593
You, you signed that boy's
death sentence.

00:10.469 --> 00:13.597
His chances of recovering from
blast crisis is zero, David.

00:13.972 --> 00:15.974
Do you refuse the chance,
no matter how small, how remote,

00:16.099 --> 00:16.975
to save a child's life?

00:17.976 --> 00:20.062
Say nothing, nothing happens.

00:22.564 --> 00:27.194
These people, Carlos, they're HIV-positive
and they never get AIDS.

00:27.861 --> 00:29.488
You can save me.

00:30.072 --> 00:32.281
How are you going to smuggle
the stem cells into the States?

00:32.573 --> 00:34.576
You're going to hide them in a
tub of butter brickle ice cream?

00:34.660 --> 00:37.287
We send them the way we send
all NorBAC samples.

00:37.496 --> 00:39.164
What the fuck is going
on here Carlos?

00:39.790 --> 00:41.375
Lloyd was my first lover.

00:42.584 --> 00:45.170
Mick, maybe this wasn't a
great idea. I--

00:45.671 --> 00:48.674
It is. It is! It's an amazing idea.

00:49.675 --> 00:52.386
It this whole whale-watching
thing just some ploy

00:52.761 --> 00:54.263
to get me in a motel room with you?

00:54.596 --> 00:56.098
Yeah, that's why I caused the blackout too.

01:00.561 --> 01:03.397
You don't understand, this is
a government operated lab I'm in now.

01:04.897 --> 01:06.400
And the paperwork.

01:09.069 --> 01:10.279
Thank you Robert.

01:10.863 --> 01:12.698
Thank you Miss Richmond.

01:13.198 --> 01:15.576
Look, I think I see a whale!
Seriously! Look, look!

01:15.784 --> 01:16.994
Mick, do you see it?

01:18.996 --> 01:19.663
Mick?

01:22.374 --> 01:23.166
Mick?

01:23.166 --> 01:24.168
Mick? Mick?

