from a sad kind of weapon */

44:17.282 --> 44:22.996
/* All of the imperfections
we perceive can start to */

44:23.622 --> 44:30.504
/* Threaten us to believe that
we can't be loved */

44:32.005 --> 44:39.012
/* When all we need is to be home */

44:42.516 --> 44:49.022
/* Hope for angels is a heart that's open */

44:50.107 --> 44:57.406
/* So far angels can't be scared away */

44:58.323 --> 45:05.789
/* Hope for angels can be
chaos and rejection */

45:06.623 --> 45:13.005
/* I'm alone for angels */

45:15.090 --> 45:18.385
/* Some of us have addictions */

45:19.011 --> 45:23.223
/* Offer aid into afflictions */

45:23.807 --> 45:30.314
/* Why do we covet pain as
our crystal path of predictions? */

45:31.023 --> 45:36.987
/* We better believe we can be loved */

45:38.197 --> 45:42.409
/* When all we need is to... */

45:42.492 --> 45:43.285
Are you there?

45:46.914 --> 45:47.998
Yeah.

45:48.790 --> 45:53.295
- I'm back 2 school 2morrow...
- "...kinda nervous."

45:56.006 --> 45:57.090
You'll be okay.

45:58.008 --> 45:59.510
(Not so sure about the school.)

46:01.512 --> 46:03.388
Get this, I think I want to
be a scientist

46:04.097 --> 46:06.099
when (if!) I grow up.

46:11.522 --> 46:14.399
"Gtg ttyl?"

46:19.404 --> 46:20.822
You're such a loser!

46:20.989 --> 46:22.699
I'll see you later.

46:48.016 --> 46:50.310
I've been offered
a senior position in another lab.

46:51.520 --> 46:52.187
Oh.

46:52.604 --> 46:55.107
- You okay? You seem a little tense.
- I'm fine!

46:55.315 --> 46:57.317
I think I see where Jill went wrong.

46:57.609 --> 46:58.819
You're Louise Raposa?

46:59.319 --> 47:01.905
Two sets of doctors said our
illness had nothing to do with Iraq.

47:02.322 --> 47:04.908
One hired by Powell
support, one by the Pentagon.

47:05.200 --> 47:06.618
- Welcome to Canada.
- Thank you.

47:07.286 --> 47:09.204
So we spent a week loading out
these bombed out buildings,

47:09.496 --> 47:11.915
even the dirt under them into these
big biohazard barrels.

47:12.207 --> 47:13.292
And what was in the buildings?

47:13.292 --> 47:16.086
Iraqi military supplies.
They wouldn't tell us more.

47:16.086 --> 47:17.713
Now 10 of us are fucking dying.

47:18.422 --> 47:21.300
They weren't exposed to anything. They were
using state of the art Hazmat gear.

47:21.592 --> 47:23.093
So the question is:
Why would you give these

47:23.594 --> 47:26.513
to a bunch of non-military,
glorified garbage collectors?

47:26.805 --> 47:28.891
We complain when people
aren't properly suited,

47:29.224 --> 47:30.601
now we're suspicious when they are?

47:30.893 --> 47:32.895
Severe anti-coagulation syndrome.

47:33.312 --> 47:35.105
- What causes it?
- We don't know.

47:35.522 --> 47:37.399
All right, why don't you two pack a bag?

